---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Sash Window Painting in Middlesex | Hancock' description='Professional sash window painting across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:460px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(9).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 55%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 64px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Sash Window Painting</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Sash Window Painting</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:520px;line-height:1.5;">The finish period properties demand. Done with the preparation that makes it last beyond one winter. Serving Windsor, Gerrards Cross, Pinner, and surrounding areas.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The problem</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Sash windows painted badly fail quickly. And replacement is expensive.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Period timber sash windows in Victorian and Edwardian properties are expensive to replace — if the originals can even be replaced in a conservation area. Proper maintenance and painting is the cost-effective alternative. Done badly, paint peels, moisture gets in, and the timber deteriorates.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Preparation is everything. Old paint needs to be back to bare timber or stable base. Knots treated. Primer applied. The right paint system — flexible enough for timber movement — applied in the right conditions.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The Hancock approach</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Strip back to sound paint. Prime. Apply the right system.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">We strip back failed paint by hand or with a heat gun — never a disc sander that damages profiles. Knot treatment on any exposed timber. Primer coat, undercoat, two finish coats minimum. We use flexible oil-based or hybrid systems appropriate for timber movement.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">We work across Windsor, Gerrards Cross, Pinner, Hatch End, and Northwood — areas with the highest concentration of period properties in the service corridor.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a sash window painting quote.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;">Fixed price. Full prep included. We assess on site.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin:28px 0 0;">Cancellations less than 48 hours before booking incur a £100 fee.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
